{"word":"G1782 - ἐντεῦθεν - enteûthen - ent-yoo'-then - Hence","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐντεῦθεν</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">enteûthen</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ent-yoo'-then</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Hence</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"இங்கிருந்து, இவ்விடம் விட்டு - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"from this place, hence"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the same as <a href=\"#/G1759 - ἐνθάδε - entháde - en-thad'-eh/1759\">G1759</a>; <i>hence</i> (literally or figuratively); (repeated) <i>on both sides:</i> - (from) hence, on either side.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}